app.curated-content-editor-explore-the-wiki-: Featured Categories allow your users to explore your community at a high level through the use of Mediawiki categories. Categories should be grouped together into logical sections such as “Films” or “Comics”. If a category doesn’t work as part of a group we suggest placing it in the Optional Categories section below.
